high_descs: Turn to the right and go to the coffee maker.
Pick up the coffee mug that is on the coffee maker.
Turn right and go to the microwave.
Open the microwave.  Put the coffee mug in the microwave.  Close the microwave door and turn it on.  When finished open the door and grab the coffee mug. Shut the door.
Turn around and go to the coffee maker.
Place the mug on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Heat up a cup of coffee in microwave.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the sink then turn left and walk to the counter and turn right to face the coffee pot.
Get the mug from under the coffee pot.
Now walk over to the microwave and stand facing it.
Warm the mug in the microwave then take it back out and close the microwave door.
Walk back over to the coffee pot.
Put the mug back where you picked it up from.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm mug under the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn right and move towards the sink then turn left and move towards the oven and then turn right and move to the coffee maker to the left of the loaf of bread.
Remove the mug from the coffee maker.
Turn right and move to the microwave next to the refrigerator and above the dishwasher.
Place the mug in the microwave, microwave the mug, then pick up the mug from the microwave.
Turn around and move towards the oven then turn right and face the loaf of bread between the sink and the coffee maker.
Place the mug in the coffee maker next to the loaf of bread.
anns.task_desc: Place a warmed mug in the coffee maker.
